column1: Please report any errors to Heather at HeatherJLeighton@gmail.com within 2 weeks of the end of the comp.
The scorers will check the cards and scoresheet against the computer systems to verify the results and
make a correction if necessary. No further changes will be made after that date.
Best lifter certificates and Participation certificates will be emailed to each competing country's manager to be
distributed to their lifters. Any corrections to spelling of names can be done by the country's manager before printing.
nb - New pers. bestlifts; n - National Record; c - Continental Record; w - World Record; cp - Competition's Record;
1..4 - Master's Record; j - Junior's Record; s - Subjunior's Record; ps. - Personally; X - the refused attempt.
DSQ - Disqualification; DR - Removed by a Doctor; TD - Technical Disqualification; DD - Doping Disqualification.
